Feature: Submit data to webdriveruniversity.com using contact us form 
		A user should submit information via the contact us form

Scenario: Submit information using the contact us form
	Given I access webdriveruniversity1
	When I click on the contact1
	And I enter first name1
	And I enter last name1
	And I enter an email address1
	And I enter comments1
	When I click on the submit button1
	Then the info should successfully be submitted via the the contact us form1
	
Scenario: Submit non valid data via the contact us form
	Given I access webdriveruniversity2
	When I click on the contact2
	And I enter non first name2
	And I enter last name2
	And I enter an email address2
	And I enter comments2
	When I click on the submit button2
	Then the info should successfully be submitted via the the contact us form2
	